text: <@U012UL77GUT> I have worked for five years at a marketing agency, mostly doing SEO and I am getting sick of writing and that type of monotonous stuff. I’m trying to learn a lot more about the job detals of other alternatives I could move into. How can I learn more about where I might be able to fit in for certain job titles Ive found as possible shifts like a creative director, digital marketing manager, social media marketing manager, and ux designer?
